<item>
            <title>[SPR-2657] There is no way to display success message(s).</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2657</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is no way to display success message(s) like struts&apos; ActionMessage. Spring should provide Messages inteface in a similar way of Errors and related tag libraries.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="15094">SPR-2657</key>
            <summary>There is no way to display success message(s).</summary>
